title: Wan Gu Shen Wang
description: 万古神王 Wan Gu Shen Wang Myriad Ancient God King Immortal God King Xu Han travelled back to his high school year. That means there are only 3 hours left before the earth goes through dramatic changes. Xu Han was slaughtered by the despicable Regal in his previous life. Now he needs to seize the chance and awaken his soul and body before other cultivators do. He will cultivate to the top and become the immortal king in the new world!
